branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The 180&#xb0; angular opening fingers can rotate back perpendicular to the gripper body for space saving and low clearance applications. While the fingers are in the 180&#xb0; retracted position, the MHW2 can move in an X-Y plane to the work location. Its unique seal design and construction protects from dust exposure and allows for a shorter overall body length.
&lt;/p&gt;

